{"tid":1594938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］其實你哋都叫人哋推文都叫咗幾個禮拜，有冇諗過⋯","createTime":"2019-09-25T22:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T11:33:05.000Z","uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fef58924c594e85a03e1f0178868f553ea149ff8","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:02:52.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過其實叫大家推文去做文宣宣傳未必真係咁有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，雖然你哋不停咁叫，文宣文係最重要， 必須要先推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">必須要知道同時承認永遠有其他人係會唔認同你嘅優次序。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地都叫咗咁多個禮拜，都有人繼續推其他文（尤其係被自殺案），係因為當你認為文宣文係最重要嘅時候，同時有其他人根本係唔認同；而佢哋個理由都唔係錯，因為今日官方已經唔會再有組織幫冤案查得水落石出而還清白。緊張呢件事嘅人，怕呢件事被滅聲，自然覺得有使命感，想將呢件事查得明明白白。你哋要點樣勸說， 都唔會令到佢哋覺得佢哋所推緊嘅文係冇咁重要。點解要勉強佢哋去放低佢哋嘅使命感同長處，去推你哋緊張過佢嘅文宣文呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁明白左呢樣冇可能有共識嘅事實，既然係咁，我哋應該諗下點樣去應付呢個情況。理論上，連登有100,000幾個用戶，有100,000幾個人才，大家各自努力，兄弟爬山，同時間做唔同嘅嘢，理論上應該係發揮到最大嘅效能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而唔係10萬個人才，逼住要做同一樣野，仲要有一半人其實唔係鍾意做、 專長做呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但點解好似做唔到？問題係連登似乎所有嘢都放喺同一個是是台入邊：推到一邊文，就推唔到第二邊文， 因為同一個台入邊，只可以得一個置頂，結果冇共識嘅前提下，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文章永遠永遠都推唔到上去，呢個根本係系統性嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n似乎大家唔係要尋求共識邊啲文重要邊啲搵次要， 而係大家明白而且接受左，大家係各自爬山嘅情況下，點唔好影響大家各自爬山嘅效果。有見及此，我覺得大家係反而要傾下，點樣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">尋求一個解決系統問題嘅共識，分台分工去最優化效能，而唔係同台多工，更加唔好全世界一台一工晒資源</span></span>。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如傾清楚以後講呢個話題嘅去呢個台，講文宣嘅留返係時事台，諸如此類。</span></span>咁樣先至可以令到各區入邊有佢自己嘅置頂重要post, 而唔係嘥時間，7x24推文同人互爭置頂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意見話，其實好多連登巴絲都只係睇熱門而唔係睇分區，我有個咁嘅拙見：連登嘅人通常跟時事都跟得好貼，佢哋未必會因為睇唔到你個項目上咗熱門而唔知道嗰個星期有乜嘢行動，會唔會更加可行嘅係考慮開發更多文宣嘅渠道，例如Facebook/IG，因為似乎Facebook嘅用戶群來講未必跟時事跟得咁貼，文宣能夠接觸佢哋，意義似乎更加大。而真係有目的地睇自己想睇嘅嘢嘅人， 自然會走入自己個區入邊去睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔喺度幾個月，只係拋磚引玉。<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講到尾</span></span>，我只係唔想大家再嘥時間勉強對方一定要推呢啲文唔推嗰啲文。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">而一齊搵吓方法尋求共識去解決呢個系統問題，</span></span>。如果你成功勸服大家當然最好，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係我見你哋已經都叫咗幾個禮拜</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。被自殺嘅事件只會越來越多，你可以叫到頭100個人聽你講去推文宣，你都唔可以叫都下100個人跟你做。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以對呢樣野諗下，發表多啲意見點樣可以幫到件事有效能啲去進行。<br />\n<br />\n（更加唔好無謂咁標籤人哋唔推呢啲文就係五毛左膠 &mdash; 傾都唔傾，唔用理性唔用腦袋就打人哋做另一邊邊，有辱連登仔聲譽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴絲耐心睇完呢篇1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06ba763d4b0ef6f9bf19ebd251b93c8354ebfd1","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"冇人覆嘅，太長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7e9c356925defb8abfc79beef519c75eb458ac","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"自推唔到⋯<br />\n<br />\n有心人過嚟講幾句，正負評，推文/不推文都好⋯"},{"pid":"47da6631039c98b4cab650778d159ad3e50f0ae6","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0617a19156fd384fe4d95ad1e75cb4c55984406","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c900b36be9eb20d8785e69963848c411cf44e10","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f132cdc7b3c1497e587be48e75ef0d70c8f701","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7d1411194eaa43d321d0fb8d0901e8a390c9e6","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"推唔郁啊，P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853d1786e64ebf51eece7482adaf40091acc8169","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"96097821e144fca082a9673ae24320c34558096b","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"日日都被自殺，要查出嚟本來係為伸張公義。文宣都有意義。唔應該互屌又話對方spin大方向。"},{"pid":"6ce9831ad5d251b9eaa39a3a869e8d4f4d692366","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"P 牌到幾時先推到文啊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f17b4a3c98dcb4b38d8c7e5ce62776669c14596b","tid":1594938,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}